    {
      "id": "E:note:row541449:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "70M h/o ulcerative colitis, coronary disease s/p MI and CABG, CVA, CRI,    Afib ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row541449#s1",
      "text": "70M h/o ulcerative colitis, coronary disease s/p MI and CABG, CVA, CRI,    Afib on coumadin, recent diagnosis cirrhosis c/b esophageal varices    presents from floor with hypotension, hypoxia, and tachypnea."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row541449:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "The    patient intitally presented one week ago on [**12-2**] with 2 days decrea",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row541449#s2",
      "text": "The    patient intitally presented one week ago on [**12-2**] with 2 days decreased    PO intake, vomiting, and bloody diarrhea. he was hypotensive at    presentation."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row541449:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "He was volume resuscitated in the ICU and treated with    cipro for empiric SBP ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row541449#s3",
      "text": "He was volume resuscitated in the ICU and treated with    cipro for empiric SBP coverage, given that a small pocket of    non-tappable ascites was detected on abdominal CT."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row541449:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "He was called out to    the floor once his blood pressures stabilized.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row541449#s4",
      "text": "He was called out to    the floor once his blood pressures stabilized."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row541449:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "On the floor, he was continued on Cipro for SBP treatment.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row541449#s5",
      "text": "On the floor, he was continued on Cipro for SBP treatment."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row541449:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "His    diuretics were held  in the setting of ARF on CRI.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row541449#s6",
      "text": "His    diuretics were held  in the setting of ARF on CRI."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row541449:7",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Cardiology was    contact[**Name (NI) **] for continued management of his systol",
      "code": null,
